ViSP 2.1.2 (Modification since ViSP 2.1.1)
  - Shared Library
	- add compilation rules for the creation of lib/libvisp-2.so
  - New Feature
	- add control for Directed Perception ptu-46 pan-tilt turret
  - Bug fix and improvement
	- vp1394Grabber settings (format, mode, framerate)
